nodes.text: A group of feral Wookiees had set up a camp on a high-rising rock formation that was accessible via large branches of the high-rising trees of the Webweaver Path level of the Rryatt Trail on the planet Kashyyyk. It consisted of several primitive huts.

The Feral Wookiee camp appeared in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
